load ../owned-harness-resume.maude

--- Coverage: a crashed turn with its persisted transcript resumes and reaches a
--- terminal.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-RESUME :
  crashed transcript
  =>* C:Cfg terminal .

--- Bite: with no persisted transcript, a crashed turn can never resume. The
--- RESIDUAL soup var means a resumed in any reachable state is a solution, so No
--- solution proves resume requires the projection.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-RESUME :
  crashed
  =>* resumed RESIDUAL:Cfg .
